3
00:00:29,625 --> 00:00:32,791
[LAFIEL]
Jinto... Jinto...

4
00:00:48,750 --> 00:00:52,541
[speaking Baronh]

5
00:00:57,708 --> 00:01:06,625
[speaking Baronh]

6
00:01:10,375 --> 00:01:15,333
[gasps, speaks Baronh]

7
00:01:15,416 --> 00:01:18,166
[coughing]

8
00:01:26,583 --> 00:01:34,541
[LAFIEL speaking Baronh]

9
00:01:37,833 --> 00:01:42,791
[speaking Baronh]

10
